        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>
                        <persName key="#Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/14">Carolus</persName> gratia Dei
                            <rs key="emperor/king">rex</rs> Francorum et Langobardorum ac <rs
                            key="patricius">patricius</rs> Romanorum. […] qualiter vir venerabilis
                            <persName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/49"
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Offersio/donatio #Abbots">
                            Anselmus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abba</rs> ex <orgName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/47"
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Offersio/donatio #Fundi #Fiscal_property #Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</orgName>, quod est constructum in honore Dei et sanctorun
                        omnium apostolorum vel Sancti Silvestri confessor Christi et Sancti
                        Benedicti abbatis in <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/38" key="#Fines"
                            >Motoninse</placeName> loco noncupante <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/15" key="#Monasteries"
                            >Nonantulas</placeName>, missa petitioni serenitate nostrae suggessit,
                        eo quod quidam <rs key="#Lombard">Langobardus</rs> nomine <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/86"
                            >Adoin</persName>, filius <persName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/89">Vectari</persName> quondam,
                        omnes res proprietatis sue, quantumcumque in territoria <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/69" key="#Fines"
                            >Vicentina</placeName> et <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/59" key="#Fines"
                            >Veroninse</placeName> ubi et ubi per singulas civitates et territoria
                        visus fuit habere, cum omni integritate ad super scriptum monasterium per
                        cartolam <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">donationis</rs> sue visus est
                        delegasse, et adserit se ipsas res cum aequitatis ordine ad partem
                        monasterii sui quieto tramite possidere. Sed pro integra firmitate petiit
                        celsitudini nostrae, ut hoc denuo circa ipsum sanctum locum ex nostra
                        indulgentia, quicquid praedictus Adoinus ad ipsam causam Dei iuste et
                        racionabiliter visus est delegasse, plenissima deliberatione cedere et
                        confirmare deberemus, sicuti pro mercedes nostrae augmentum visi sumus
                        fecisse. Quapropter per presentem auctoritatem nostram decernimus ac
                        iubemus, ut inspecta ipsa donatione praedicti Adoini quondam, sicut per eam
                        declaratur quicquid ad praephatum monasterium iusto tramite delegavit,
                        deinceps per hoc nostrum serenitatis atque confirmationis praeceptum ad
                        ipsum sanctum locum perpetualiter proficiat in augmentis. Et specialiter
                        concedimus ad super scriptum monasterium pro anime nostrae salutem res illas
                        in territurio <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/7"
                            >Bononiense</placeName>, quas <persName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Fiscal_property #Emperor/king"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/12">Liutprandus quondam
                            rex</persName>
                        <persName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fiscal_property #Extended_household_of"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/88">Gregorio quondam
                                <persName>Greco</persName> iocatori</persName> suo et eius filiis
                        per suum confirmavit <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">praeceptum</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property">Caldario</placeName> et <placeName
                            key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property"> Cesaretico</placeName> et fundo
                            <placeName key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property"> Casa Novola</placeName>, sicut
                        ipse Gregorius per praeceptum ante dicti Liutprandi regis vel per <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">enfiteusi</rs> tenuit et postea
                        iure legitimo nostro devenerunt dominio in integrum, ita ut ab hodiernum
                        diem ante dictus Anselmus abba suique successores, qui fuerint rectores in
                        ipso monasterio, vel monachi inibi sub sancta regula consistentes per hanc
                        nostram auctoritatem habeant concessum, quatenus melius eis delectet pro
                        nobis vel pro stabilitate regni nostri adtentius Domini misericordiam
                        exorare. Et ut haec praeceptio atque confirmatio firmior habeantur et
                        diuturnis temporibus melius conservetur, manu propria subter firmavimus et
                        de anulo nostro sigillari iussimus. Signum Caroli gloriosissimi regis
                            <persName key="#Chancellor">Ercanbaldus</persName> relegi et sub […]
                        Actum <placeName key="#Palatium" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/83"
                            >Aquis palatio publico</placeName>. […] </ab>
